# Actual Size on Screen — V1 Core Engine Implementation Plan

> **Scope**: Build the best possible Actual Size Engine. Nothing else.
> **Strategy**: Incremental replacement — existing template stays live until new engine is proven.

---

## What V1 Delivers

| ✅ In Scope | ❌ Deferred to V2 |
|---|---|
| Calibration system (3 methods) | Search |
| Rendering engine (CSS-variable driven) | User contributions |
| Object data structure + TypeScript schema | Ads/monetisation |
| Dynamic routes for categories + objects | Comparison mode |
| Reusable `ActualSizeViewer` component | API endpoints |
| SEO: titles, JSON-LD, sitemap | Brand/domain changes |
| Performance: 95+ Lighthouse | Social features |
| 3 starter data sets (~30 objects) | 100+ objects |

