## Incremental Replacement Strategy

Existing files are **never deleted** in V1. New components are built alongside them. The homepage is updated last, only after the engine is proven working in isolation.

```
Phase A: Build engine in isolation (new files only, no existing file touched)
Phase B: Wire engine into a single test route (/test)
Phase C: Build real routes ([category], [category]/[slug])
Phase D: Replace homepage last
```

