### Sitemap Strategy

`src/pages/sitemap.xml.ts` dynamically generates entries for:
- All category pages (priority 0.8)
- All object pages (priority 0.6, `<lastmod>` from `updatedAt`)
- Static pages: home (1.0), calibration (0.7)

Requires `@astrojs/sitemap` integration + `site` set in `astro.config.mjs`.

### Internal Linking Map

```
Homepage → all Category pages (footer nav + category tabs)
Category → all its Object pages (grid)
Object → 3–5 related objects (relatedSlugs field)
Object → its Category page (breadcrumb)
```

Every object page has at least 5 inbound internal links by the time we have 30+ objects.

